OL,6,FUTV has uncovered footage from almost
OL,7,F50 years ago showing a 10-year
OL,8,Fhaemophiliac being injected with
OL,9,FFactor 8 - hailed as "wonder
OL,10,Ftreatment" at the time, which turned
OL,11,Fout to be very far from the actual
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,FToday the Prime Minister offered an
OL,15,F"unequivocal apology" describing the
OL,16,Finfected blood scandal as something
OL,17,Fwhich should "shake our nation to the
OL,18,Fcore".
OL,20,FRishi Sunak promised "comprehensive
OL,21,Fcompensation" no matter the cost.
