OL,6,FPaul Kirkpatrick now in his 50s has
OL,7,Flived much of his life with Hepatitis
OL,8,FC - a blood borne virus contracted by
OL,9,Fthousands of people treated by the NHS
OL,10,Fin the 1970s and 1980s.
OL,12,F"We're looking at a video from our
OL,13,Ffilm clips from 1976. Now in 2024 and
OL,14,Fin May 2024 we are still losing
OL,15,Fpeople," Paul told UTV after watching
OL,16,Fthe footage for the very first time
OL,17,Fsince it was broadcast.
