OL,6,FOne of the thousands of victims of the
OL,7,Fscandal to have died is Paul's older
OL,8,Fbrother Desmond - he too received
OL,9,Fcontaminated blood products and died
OL,10,Fsuddenly with cancer 10 years ago.
OL,12,F"The diagnosis changed within two or
OL,13,Fthree days from a treatable cancer to
OL,14,Fa life ending cancer," Paul said,
OL,15,Fdescribing Desmond's liver and stomach
OL,16,Fas being 'riddled' with the disease.
