OL,6,F"The Inquiry brought in medical
OL,7,Fexperts and he gave me a good rational
OL,8,Fexplanation explanation around it
OL,9,Fbecause no one should die in this day
OL,10,Fand age that quickly."
OL,12,F"3,000 people, a generation of
OL,13,Fhaemophilias are being wiped out
OL,14,Fthrough getting treatment... supposed
OL,15,Fto help you rather than kill you."
