OL,6,FPaul and Desmond were cared for at the
OL,7,FRoyal Victoria Hospital in Belfast
OL,8,Fwhere they received Factor 8
OL,9,Ftreatment, which was revolutionary for
OL,10,Fits time in that it allowed patients
OL,11,Fto be treated for bleeds at home.
OL,13,FThe feature, filmed by UTV, was
OL,14,Fdesigned to highlight the life
OL,15,Fchanging qualities of the treatment
OL,16,Fwhich was often termed a 'miracle
OL,17,Fdrug.'
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/10
