OL,6,FPaul and Desmond, like many other
OL,7,Fpatients, were treated by the late Dr
OL,8,FElizabeth Mayne, Northern Ireland's
OL,9,FConsultant Haemotologist.
OL,11,FIn the footage from 1976, Dr Mayne is
OL,12,Fpressed by a UTV reporter as to
OL,13,Fwhether there are any problems with
OL,14,Frejection in relation to Factor 8.
OL,16,F"There really is very little in terms
OL,17,Fof rejection. We always stick to the
OL,18,Fpatient's blood group," Dr Mayne told
OL,19,Fthe reporter.
