OL,6,F"In any blood transfusion that any
OL,7,Fpatient receives, there is always a
OL,8,Frisk of getting a virus causing
OL,9,Fjaundice, a virus, hepatitis.
OL,11,F"When we come to the commercial, or
OL,12,Fthe very concentrated Factor 8, this
OL,13,Fhas been harvested from perhaps
OL,14,Fthousands of donors and put through a
OL,15,Fmanufacturing process and therefore
OL,16,Fthey hope very much that they will
OL,17,Fhave diluted out the risk in one
OL,18,Fsense," she explained.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G7/10
